1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:49,500
Seven years ago,

2
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:51,330
the Yunzhou Governor's mansion

3
00:00:51,330 --> 00:00:52,730
was wiped out overnight.

4
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:55,060
There were no bodies at the scene,

5
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:56,160
only bloodstains.

6
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:59,260
The court closed the case as a supernatural disturbance,

7
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:00,460
and sealed the files.

8
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:05,960
My Lord.

9
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:10,430
The head of the department explicitly ordered these files sealed.

10
00:01:15,660 --> 00:01:18,760
Rumor has it there were ghosts involved in that case.

11
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,500
Cinnabar.

12
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:34,860
At 11:45 PM,

13
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,430
seven souls locked,

14
00:01:36,860 --> 00:01:38,060
guided by blood jade,

15
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:40,430
never to cross into reincarnation.

16
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,460
Cinnabar mixed with blood

17
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:56,100
reveals itself when heated.

18
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:58,000
It's not a ghost, it's human.

19
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,990
Someone deliberately left clues.

20
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,600
Whether it is a clue or a warning

21
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,600
remains unknown.

22
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,160
Put the files away properly.

23
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,900
My Lord, where are you going?

24
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:08,699
To the morgue.

25
00:02:09,229 --> 00:02:10,430
It is almost 11:45 PM.

26
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,460
If the files are a warning,

27
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:14,520
they will surely make a move tonight.

28
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,760
My Lord, wait for me. I will go too.

29
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:27,990
Registrar Shen.

30
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,460
There is only bloody water and a strange jade in the coffin.

31
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,630
No bodies, no bones.

32
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,560
I have been examining bodies for 30 years,

33
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,760
and have never seen anything like this.

34
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:57,000
The Criminal Investigation Department will take this case.

35
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,230
The patterns on this blood jade

36
00:02:58,230 --> 00:02:59,300
are exactly the same

37
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,560
as the evidence from the Yunzhou case my father was investigating

38
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,890
before he disappeared.

39
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,160
This is not blood.

40
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,400
It's red phosphorus powder

41
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,260
mixed with rust and madder juice.

42
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,260
This powder has uniform granules

43
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,360
and extremely high purity.

44
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,730
It is specially supplied by the armory

45
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:14,790
for night signals.

46
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:20,100
All seven coffins are the same. The warm liquid inside

47
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,760
accelerated the reaction of the red phosphorus powder,

48
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,860
creating bubbles to simulate the illusion of boiling blood.

49
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,730
Someone used this method to create a bizarre scene,

50
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:28,400
covering up their true purpose

51
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,130
of stealing the seven corpses.

52
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,760
You said no one came near last night.

53
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,430
Did you hear any strange noises?

54
00:03:38,430 --> 00:03:39,329
After 11 PM,

55
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,200
there were indeed thumping sounds.

56
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:44,860
It sounded like coffin lids rattling.

57
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:46,860
I thought it was a stray cat,

58
00:03:46,930 --> 00:03:48,160
so I didn't dare come out to check.

59
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,600
Since you are the morgue keeper,

60
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,430
hearing strange noises from the coffins but not daring to check

61
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,100
is unreasonable.

62
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:53,060
I...

63
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:54,060
I just had a moment of weakness

64
00:03:54,060 --> 00:03:56,400
and occasionally stole some lamp oil from the morgue to sell.

65
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,460
As for the coffins,

66
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,560
I really didn't do it!

67
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:19,100
The recurrence of the methods from the Yunzhou case seven years ago

68
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,700
is by no means a coincidence.

69
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,460
Stealing lamp oil.

70
00:04:28,330 --> 00:04:30,160
But your hands and the dirt under your fingernails

71
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,560
are completely clean.

72
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,260
This shows you were only walking around normally

73
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:35,460
and didn't touch the coffins or carry heavy objects.

74
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:37,430
Stealing lamp oil is a trivial matter.

75
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:38,860
Your eagerness to confess

76
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:39,560
makes you suspicious.

77
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,000
You are the mortuary guard,

78
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,100
and seven bodies were stolen during your watch.

79
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,159
This is a felony.

80
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:45,700
If you don't tell the truth

81
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,159
and help me find the truth,

82
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,600
you will be exiled for 3,000 miles at least,

83
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,030
or beheaded at worst.

84
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,560
My Lord, have mercy!

85
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,730
I will tell the truth.

86
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,460
Last night at midnight,

87
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:55,100
a few people did climb over the wall.

88
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,760
They gave me ten taels of silver

89
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:59,730
and told me to say no one came near.

90
00:04:59,730 --> 00:05:00,760
They also threatened me

91
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,860
that if I dared to expose them,

92
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:03,130
they would kill my whole family.

93
00:05:03,130 --> 00:05:04,200
What did they look like?

94
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,400
They were all masked,

95
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:07,160
but the leader's

96
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,420
waist tag was partially exposed.

97
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:11,530
It was the style of the Imperial City Department.

98
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:12,990
I would never be mistaken.

99
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:13,960
Since the Imperial City Department is involved,

100
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,090
this case will be hard to investigate.

101
00:05:18,330 --> 00:05:19,830
The involvement of the Imperial City Department

102
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:21,630
only shows that there's more to this case.

103
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:23,230
They set up this trap,

104
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,630
stole seven bodies,

105
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:26,660
and used the name of the Imperial City Department to exert pressure.

106
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,600
They must have an ulterior motive.

107
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,060
And this blood chalcedony

108
00:05:29,530 --> 00:05:31,190
is the key to solving the case.

109
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:34,700
Gu of Yunzhou.

110
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:36,960
This is an old item belonging to Gu Wenyuan,

111
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,760
the missing Prefect of Yunzhou from seven years ago.

112
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,500
The body theft, the conspiracy,

113
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,860
and the involvement of the Imperial City Department

114
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:45,720
are all related to the disappearance of Gu Wenyuan.

115
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:50,830
This fiber was extracted from the gap of the coffin.

116
00:05:51,230 --> 00:05:52,260
It has a fine texture

117
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:54,360
and is a brocade exclusively used for official uniforms.

118
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,830
The pattern of this brocade

119
00:05:56,830 --> 00:06:00,100
is identical to the uniform of the Criminal Cases Department.

120
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:00,960
Mo'er.

121
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,500
Remember.

122
00:06:03,130 --> 00:06:07,760
Some jade is stained with blood and tied to lives.

123
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:12,500
Is this what you were investigating back then?

124
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:21,130
Tomorrow,

125
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:23,300
we will go and meet the Director.

126
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:40,030
Someone touched the blood chalcedony.

127
00:06:40,030 --> 00:06:40,900
Investigate it.
